{
  "stem": "17301.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 114.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And once the mattresses were all stuffed, we found out those were for us to sleep on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because we had two barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One was the navy blue dress barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "One was the-- the red dress barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And following day, they took us into this barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the site was only-- and the stench was unreal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We saw clothing all the way to the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was like a barn, all the way to the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they told us, you have to take one piece at a time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And take the hemline apart, and take the-- the buttons that were covered.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "If we saw any covered buttons, we had to take the covered buttons apart.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because what we found out, a lot of the covered buttons had gold pieces in them instead of being buttons.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This is how they were hoping that they'll be able to utilize their monies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I found out that all this clothing was-- came from the cattle cars, and from the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And this is what we start to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We had to separate men's, women's, and children's clothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They had like handbags, leather handbags.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We had to cut them open, because on the bottom of a lot of the handbags they had a lot of jewelries tucked in-- inside.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So we had to take those apart, the hemlines apart.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And whatever was suspicious, wherever we thought that there could be some jewelry in, we had to take.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we found a lot of very valuable jewelry in them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And naturally, we had to put that in a box, and we had to turn it over to the German.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Because every day, after we were through working, they came around to get all the jewelry from us.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
